query:
/*+  */ select count(*)
from question AS q1
inner join tag_question AS tq1
on q1.id = tq1.question_id AND q1.view_count >= 10 AND q1.view_count <= 1000
inner join tag AS t1
on t1.id = tq1.tag_id AND t1.name IN ('acid-base',
'bugs',
'differential-equations',
'export',
'functions',
'graphics',
'graphs-and-networks',
'inorganic-chemistry',
'matrix',
'numerics',
'performance-tuning',
'physical-chemistry',
'plotting')
inner join answer AS a1
on q1.id = a1.question_id
inner join so_user AS u1
on a1.owner_user_id = u1.id AND u1.reputation >= 10 AND u1.reputation <= 100000
inner join site AS s
on s.site_id = tq1.site_id AND s.site_id = q1.site_id AND s.site_id = a1.site_id AND s.site_id = u1.site_id AND s.site_id = t1.site_id AND s.site_name IN ('chemistry',
'graphicdesign',
'mathematica')
inner join badge AS b
on b.user_id = u1.id AND s.site_id = b.site_id AND b.name ilike '%re%'
inner join account AS acc
on acc.id = u1.account_id;
